50|$|On October 5, 2009, Joseph Stiglitz {{said that}} any new tax should be levied on all asset classes - not merely foreign exchange, {{and would be}} based on the gross value of the assets, thereby helping to {{discourage}} the creation of <b>asset</b> <b>bubbles.</b>|$|R
